code: @Test public void testLoadedCustomLogbackConfig() throws Exception {     SampleLogbackApplication.main(new String[0]).     assertThat(this.output.toString()).contains("Sample Debug Message").     assertThat(this.output.toString()).doesNotContain("Sample Trace Message"). }

@Test public void testProfile() throws Exception {     SampleLogbackApplication.main(new String[] { "--spring.profiles.active=staging" }).     assertThat(this.output.toString()).contains("Sample Debug Message").     assertThat(this.output.toString()).contains("Sample Trace Message"). }
